## Code Simplification Report

### Changes Made

#### 1. Eliminate duplicate `isOverdue` call in DetailPanel
**File**: `frontend/src/components/DetailPanel.tsx:134,207-208`
**Type**: Removed redundancy / eliminated duplicate call
**Before**:
```tsx
  const colors = typeColorClasses(thing?.type_hint ?? null)

  return (
    ...
    {thing.checkin_date && (
      <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 ${isOverdue(thing.checkin_date) ? 'text-ideas font-semibold' : ''}`}>
        <span className="shrink-0">{isOverdue(thing.checkin_date) ? '\u26a0' : '\ud83d\udcc5'}</span>
```
**After**:
```tsx
  const checkinOverdue = thing?.checkin_date ? isOverdue(thing.checkin_date) : false

  return (
    ...
    {thing.checkin_date && (
      <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 ${checkinOverdue ? 'text-ideas font-semibold' : ''}`}>
        <span className="shrink-0">{checkinOverdue ? '\u26a0' : '\ud83d\udcc5'}</span>
```

The PR had removed an IIFE that computed `overdue` once, but replaced it with two identical calls to `isOverdue(thing.checkin_date)` in consecutive lines. This restores single-computation without the IIFE by extracting to a `const` before the return.

